text.section:
The institution-specific plan shall address:
Accurate bed count data for licensed beds and staffed and operated beds;
Cost data associated with all hospital beds and associated services on a hospital-specific basis;
Migration patterns and current and future projected population data;
Accessibility and availability of beds;
Quality of care;
Current health care needs, as well as growth trends for such needs, for the area served by each hospital;
Hospitals in high growth areas; and
Utilization.
